'''南極長城'''（'''SPW'''，The South Pole Wall）是由[[星系|星系]]組成的[[大尺度纖維狀結構|大尺度纖維狀結構]]，位在5億光年之外，延伸至少13.7億光年的一個巨大[[可觀測宇宙#大尺度結構|宇宙結構]]<ref name="APJ-20200710">{{cite journal |author=Pomarède, Daniel |display-authors=et al. |title=Cosmicflows-3: The South Pole Wall |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/1538-4357/ab9952 |date=10 July 2020 |journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] |volume=897 |number=2 |doi=10.3847/1538-4357/ab9952 |accessdate=10 July 2020 |arxiv=2007.04414 |archive-date=2020-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809143115/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.3847/1538-4357/ab9952 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HARV-202001">{{cite news |author=Pomerede, D. |display-authors=et al. |title=The South Pole Wall |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2020AAS...23545301P/abstract |date=January 2020 |work=[[Harvard_University|Harvard University]] |accessdate=10 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918135607/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2020AAS...23545301P/abstract |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HW-20200710">{{cite news |author=Staff |title=Astronomers map massive structure beyond Laniakea Supercluster |url=https://www.hawaii.edu/news/2020/07/10/laniakea-supercluster-mapping/ |date=10 July 2020 |work=[[University_of_Hawaii|University of Hawaii]] |accessdate=10 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125184600/https://www.hawaii.edu/news/2020/07/10/laniakea-supercluster-mapping/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20200710">{{cite news |last=Overbye |first=Dennis |author-link=Dennis Overbye |title=Beyond the Milky Way, a Galactic Wall - Astronomers have discovered a vast assemblage of galaxies hidden behind our own, in the "zone of avoidance." |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/10/science/astronomy-galaxies-attractor-universe.html |date=10 July 2020 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |accessdate=10 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214221534/http://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/10/science/astronomy-galaxies-attractor-universe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="LS-20200709">{{cite news |last=Mann |first=Adam |title=Astronomers discover South Pole Wall, a gigantic structure stretching 1.4 billion light-years across |url=https://www.livescience.com/south-pole-wall-discovered-in-space.html |date=10 July 2020 |work=[[Live_Science|Live Science]] |accessdate=10 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113173432/https://www.livescience.com/south-pole-wall-discovered-in-space.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SA-20200714">{{cite news |last=Starr |first=Michelle |title=A Giant 'Wall' of Galaxies Has Been Found Stretching Across The Universe |url=https://www.sciencealert.com/a-giant-wall-of-galaxies-has-been-found-stretching-across-the-universe |date=14 July 2020 |work=ScienceAlert.com |accessdate=19 July 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205141100/https://www.sciencealert.com/a-giant-wall-of-galaxies-has-been-found-stretching-across-the-universe |dead-url=no }}</ref>。從天文的角度來看，這個結構在5個地方，包括一個非常接近[[天極|南天極]]，都很密集。根據發現這個長城的國際天文團隊的說法：「……是當地體積最大的連續特徵，可與[[史隆長城|史隆長城]]相媲美，但距離只有一半」<ref name="APJ-20200710" />。它的發現是由[[巴黎-薩克雷大學|巴黎-薩克雷大學]]的丹尼爾·波馬雷德和[[R·布倫特·塔利|李察·布倫特·塔利]]以及[[夏威夷大學|夏威夷大學]]的同事在2020年7月宣佈的<ref name="APJ-20200710" />。波馬雷德解釋說：「人們可能會想，這麼大而不是那麼遙遠的結構怎麼會被忽視。這是因為它在一個尚未被完整測量過的天空區域，對那裏的觀測直接受到銀河系的塵埃和星雲的前景斑塊阻礙」<ref name="HW-20200710" />。

== 尺度 ==
長城的長度超過13.7億[[光年|光年]]，橫艮在5億光年之外的一片廣大區域<ref name="NYT-20200710" /><ref name="LS-20200709" />。這巨大的結構，至少有一小部分，位於[[銀河系|銀河系]]的[[隱帶|隱帶]]（或[[隱帶|銀河遮蔽區]]）後面<ref name="SA-20200714" /><ref name="QU-20200711">{{cite news |last=O'Reilly |first=Aaron |title=Is the zone of galactic obscuration, that is beyond the cosmic south pole wall, the edge of our sub-reality? Or is the boundary where decoherence stops being a thing? |url=https://www.quora.com/Is-the-zone-of-galactic-obscuration-that-is-beyond-the-cosmic-south-pole-wall-the-edge-of-our-sub-reality-Or-is-the-boundary-where-decoherence-stops-being-a-thing |date=11 July 2020 |work=[[Quora|Quora]] |accessdate=19 July 2020 }} 註解："簡單的說，銀河遮蔽區就是被銀河系的中心本身遮蔽，使觀測正在發生的事變得非常困難的區域。這純粹是由我們相對於銀河中心的位置來定義的，本身並不是一個實際的物體。"</ref>。大尺度纖維狀結構從北天的[[英仙座|英仙座]]，經過天南極附近，到達南天遙遠的[[望遠鏡座|望遠鏡座]]。它是如此的巨大，因此受到[[宇宙膨脹|局部的宇宙膨脹]]很大的影響<ref name="NYT-20200710" />。 據天文學家塔利說：「我們懷疑南極長城是否比我們看到的要大得多。我們繪製的地圖覆蓋了我們調查過的整個地區。我們是宇宙的早期探險家，將我們的地圖延伸到未知的領域」<ref name="HW-20200710" />。根據發現它的天文學家的說法：「在我們以更大的尺度繪製宇宙地圖之前，我們無法確定它的完整範圍，也無法確定它是否不同尋常」<ref name="LS-20200709" />。

